<li>Mackenzie, Dana. "Communication speed nears terminal velocity". <i>New Scientist</i> 187.2507 (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2005-07-09"><a href="/wiki/July_9" title="July 9">9 July</a> <a href="/wiki/2005" title="2005">2005</a></span>): 38–41. ISSN 0262-4079.</li>
<li>Wicker, Stephen B. <i>Error Control Systems for Digital Communication and Storage</i>. Englewood Cliffs, N.J.: Prentice-Hall, 1995. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0132008092" class="internal">ISBN 0-13-200809-2</a>.</li>
<li>Wilson, Stephen G. <i>Digital Modulation and Coding</i>, Englewood Cliffs, N.J.: Prentice-Hall, 1996. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0132100711" class="internal">ISBN 0-13-210071-1</a>.</li>
